Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.03,0:26:05.79,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H1C1B1B&}像坚毅盛开的花朵一般
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.53,0:26:16.49,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H1C1B1B&}无论何时都用尽全力去活着
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.33,0:26:26.33,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H1C1B1B&}所以 把门打开吧 去描绘未来吧
